                     <interp inst="t18310106-44-person460" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a Policeman. I saw the prisoner come out of the prosecutor's premises, and immediately took him - I asked what he had in his hat; he said Nothing - I took it off, and there was nothing; I took him into the shop, and found the bristles inside his trousers.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
